            <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/using_git_hooks_with_dita.dita" xtrc="p:6;121:16">Git automatically populates the <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/using_git_hooks_with_dita.dita" xtrc="codeph:3;121:56">.git/hooks</codeph> directory with example
