            <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/using_git_hooks_with_dita.dita" xtrc="p:11;182:16">To fix this, I had to go inside <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/using_git_hooks_with_dita.dita" xtrc="filepath:4;182:58">{dita.ot.dir}/bin/dita</filepath> and
